## Any other business

Bdale and Joerg were asked about their investigations into obtaining an
intermediate SSL CA for SPI. Their overall verdict was that it was too
little benefit for too much money for  Their overall verdict was that it
was too little benefit for too much money for SPI to get involved with
being a proper CA at present. OFTC's immediate needs for an SSL
certificate had been dealt with via the purchase of a specific cert.

